{"tid":1833062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要的事要講無數次］721係最重要既事件","createTime":"2020-01-21T15:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T15:52:25.000Z","uid":19945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"258656787b8762d7e448c0df0b9d3b9c99e22b0d","tid":1833062,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"點解一定要提住721？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721係政府永遠迴避唔到既責任</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">721係鄉黑合作既真實證據</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">721係區分人類同畜生既照妖鏡</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">721係連美國都開聲要追究既事件</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家可以覺得攰<br />\n太多事件會有想逃避既一刻<br />\n但唯獨721唔可以 事件發生左半年有多<br />\n太多影片太多個案未來係好難全部追究到<br />\n但721係切切實實放在眼前既錯誤<br />\n絕對唔會走到數 點解個兩個指揮官收哂皮唔蒲頭<br />\n因為不論到時係香港人贏定政權搵替死鬼降溫<br />\n721對雙方都係首要任務<br />\n所以大家記得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一生不忘721</strong></span>"},{"pid":"ea12c449a3299d6dc649db505f42a8cc66212153","tid":1833062,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"而且721係暫時香港人最堅持既事件<br />\n老實講開真槍又好樂同琳都好<br />\n係真係愈來愈少人提<br />\n唯獨721係仍然堅持"},{"pid":"b8cf82a1581c4e34f603f45705581bd1055c634a","tid":1833062,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"4f72cefca9b58cb2a3aa12f1fa7aae6d155eb1be","tid":1833062,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:49:54.000Z","msg":"你睇班狗搞鳩721集會就知"},{"pid":"5268ecc4d7074f5ea32eacb607b3e7b5c85b506d","tid":1833062,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"721"}]}